General.Name: Smart Eye AB
General.Description: Smart Eye AB (publ) develops human insight artificial intelligence technology solutions that understands, supports, and predicts human behavior in the Nordics countries, rest of Europe, North America, Asia, and internationally. The company offers driver monitoring systems and interior sensing solutions for automotive market; and driver monitoring systems that include hardware and software for fleet, aftermarket, and small volume OEMs. It also provides various behavioral research products, including smart eye research instruments under the Smart Eye Pro, AI-X, XO, and Aurora names, as well as offers smart recorders, software, and analysis services to automotive, aviation and aerospace, media and marketing, psychology and neuroscience, and behavioral research industries. Smart Eye AB (publ) was incorporated in 1999 and is headquartered in Gothenburg, Sweden.
